ess|year=1827|location=Bhopal|url=https://books.google.com/?id=hqE8AAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false|ref=harv}}\n* {{Citation|title=Land Acquisition Act|last=Government of Maharashtra|year=1961|location=Bombay|url=http://maharashtra.gov.in/data/gr/english/1961/01/24/20061116122835001.pdf}}\n* {{Citation|title=Political and Military Events in British India: From the Years 1756 to 1849|volume=Volume 1 Political and Military Events in British India: From the Years 1756 to 1849|first=William|last=Hough|publisher=W.H. Allen & Company|year=1853|location=London|oclc=5105166|url=https://books.google.com/?id=CI0cAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false}}\n* {{Citation|title=A Brief History of the Indian Peoples|first=Sir William Wilson|last=Hunter|year=1907|publisher=Clarendon Press|location=Oxford|oclc=464656679|url=https://books.google.com/?id=koUqAAAAYAAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false}}\n* {{Citation|title=Imperial Gazetteer of India.|volume=Volume 2 of Imperial Gazetteer of India, Great Britain. India Office Gazetteers of British India, 1833\u20131962|first=Sir William Wilson|last=Hunter|editor1=James Sutherland Cotton|editor2=Sir Richard Burn|editor3=Sir William Stevenson Meyer|publisher=Clarendon Press|year=1909|location=Oxford|url=https://books.google.com/?id=UT0KAQAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false}}\n* {{Citation|title=A Handbook for Travellers in India, Burma, and Ceylon|last= Murray |first=John|publisher=[[John Murray (publisher)|John Murray]]|year=1901|location=Calcutta|oclc=222574206|url=https://books.google.com/?id=zFYoAAAAYAAJ&dq=battle+of+kirkee+loss}}\n* {{Citation|title=A History of India: From the Earliest Times to the Present Day|first=Thomas|last=Keightley|publisher=Whittaker|year=1847|location=London|url=https://books.google.com/?id=bYAfAAAAYAAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false}}\n* {{Citation|title=The Calcutta Review|volume=119|first=Madhav Rao Venayek|last=Kibe|year=1904|location=Calcutta; London|ur